snippet: A compromise defense policy bill in Congress would bar the purchase of more Russian-made rocket engines to launch U.S. military satellites, clearing the way for competitive bids for 14 future launches, senior congressional aides said on Tuesday....

headline.print_headline: Bill Would Cap Russian Engines on U.S. Satellite Launches
headline.main: Bill Would Cap Russian Engines on U.S. Satellite Launches

lead_paragraph: A compromise defense policy bill in Congress would bar the purchase of more Russian-made rocket engines to launch U.S. military satellites, clearing the way for competitive bids for 14 future launches, senior congressional aides said on Tuesday.
